### Get all products (with API key)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products
X-API-Key: dev-key-12345
Accept: application/json

### Get all products (without API key - should fail)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific product
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/1
X-API-Key: dev-key-12345
Accept: application/json

### Create a new product (with validation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
X-API-Key: dev-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Mouse Pro",
  "description": "High-precision gaming mouse with RGB lighting and customizable buttons",
  "price": 89.99,
  "category": "electronics",
  "inStock": true
}

### Create a product with validation errors
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
X-API-Key: dev-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "Invalid product",
  "price": -10,
  "category": "invalid-category",
  "inStock": "not-boolean"
}

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/1
X-API-Key: dev-key-12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Super Gaming Laptop",
  "price": 1499.99
}

### Delete a product (admin permission required)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/2
X-API-Key: admin-key-abcdef
Accept: application/json

### Test 404 route
GET http://localhost:3000/api/nonexistent
X-API-Key: dev-key-12345
